on reading compounds: 臈【ロウ】year in the Buddhist order (after the completion of the first meditation retreat), becoming more experienced with age, social status based on this experience
臈たける【ロウタケル】to be elegant (usu. of a woman), to be graceful, to be refined, to become well-experienced, to mature
女郎【ジョロウ】prostitute (esp. Edo period)
劫臈【コウロウ】long time, long years of service
